<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT71">
<l>cēya ṉaṇiyaṉ ciṟiyaṉ mikapperiya</l>
<l>ṉāyaṉ tuvaraikkō ṉāyṉiṉṟa māyaṉaṉ</l>
<l>ṟōtiya vākkataṉaik kallā rulakatti</l>
<l>lētilarāy meyññāṉa mil.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those words uttered on that day by the Dark [Lord]</l>
<l>who is distant, nearby, small, very big, the Cowherd,</l>
<l rend="indent">the King of Dvārakā—</l>
<l>Those who do not know [them] in [this] world</l>
<l>are [God’s] enemies devoid of true knowledge.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
